tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_execution_logs (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    buy_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    sell_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    volume INT,
    profit DECIMAL(12, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_logs (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  execution_time TIMESTAMP,
  security_name VARCHAR(255),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_logs (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    trader_name VARCHAR(50),
    executed_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    executed_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_history (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT REFERENCES trade_execution_logs(trade_id),
    transaction_date DATE,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(10),
    transaction_amount DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE arbitrage_strategies (
    strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(50),
    potential_profit DECIMAL(10,2),
    risk_level VARCHAR(10),
    strategy_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE TradeExecutionLogs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  trade_date DATE,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  execution_price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE TradeHistory (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  trader_name VARCHAR(50),
  trade_date DATE,
  stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  executed_price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE TransactionDetails (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  trade_id INT,
  execution_log_id INT,
  strategy_id INT,
  execution_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_execution_logs (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    executed_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id INT,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    executed_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    partner_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES trade_partners(partner_id)
);

CREATE TABLE trade_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    strategy_id INT,
    result VARCHAR(50),
    FOREIGN KEY (trade_id) REFERENCES trade_execution_logs(trade_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (strategy_id) REFERENCES arbitrage_strategies(strategy_id)
);
